It's just a few things in bullet form, because even if I want to be distracted I know I'll have to get back to my thesis document eventually.
<ul><li>Pimping # 1: <a target="new" href="http://adettenotadeth.tumblr.com/">In which everything jumbles together</a>, a.k.a. my Tumblr account. It's disorganized, with a bit of anything and everything I'm interested in. But that's what makes it so fun. XD I reblog a lot, though if I feel like making GIFs I post them there as well.</li><li>Pimping # 2: I'd like to get some opinions and possibly constructive criticism (concrit) on <a href="http://adettenotadeth.tumblr.com/post/5570603994/location-singapore-botanic-gardens-date-and">this photo</a> I took during my trip in Singapore. I really love this photo but I also know it's not the best so I'd like to know what people really think about it.</li><li>Pimping # 3: Do you love Arashi? Do you love singing and dancing along with Arashi songs?!? Do you love watching other fans sing and dance along with Arashi songs?!?!? Then join in the fun of <lj user="araoke" /> ! :D It's a sister comm of <lj user="g_clef_no_arash" /> that caters solely to karaoke and dance covers of Arashi's songs. Community membership is always open, unless it gets too rowdy (read: too much wank) and we'll have to close the club temporarily.</li></ul>Okay, back to work now. Lame post is lame.

